pageContext.claim: “HIGHEST CABLE TELEVISION RATINGS OF ALL TIME. SECOND HIGHEST OVERALL TELEVISION RATINGS OF ALL TIME. Some day these Fake Media Companies are going to miss me, very badly!!!”
pageContext.analysis: The president loves good TV ratings, but he did not hit the mark he set for himself. The first debate between former vice president Joe Biden and President Trump was the third most watched televised debate, according to Nielsen.
